{"subject":"Economics",'year':2017,"question":"Portfolio investment is:",'options':['Purchase of foreign stocks and bonds','Purchase of foreign factories','Direct control over foreign business','Long-term loans'],'correctIndex':0,"explanation":"Portfolio is financial assets without control."},
